				returnType = 'cmdb_ci_ni_logical_path';
				break;
			case 'PHYSICAL':
				returnType = 'cmdb_ci_ni_physical_link';
				break;
			case 'NETWORK INTERFACE':
				returnType = 'cmdb_ci_ni_interface';
				break;
		}
